      <title>法国经济增长疲弱正在破坏马克龙的预算计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/french-economy-latest-weak-growth-undermines-macron-budget-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据统计机构 Insee 的最新预测，法国经济正在努力实现总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 所需的增长，以兑现控制预算赤字的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/french-economy-latest-weak-growth-undermines-macron-budget-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利赢得与辞职银行家的 140 万欧元法国奖金纠纷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/morgan-stanley-wins-1-4-million-french-bonus-spat-with-banker-who-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利赢得了一场法庭诉讼，推翻了向一位董事总经理支付的 140 万欧元（合 150 万美元）的延期奖金，这位董事总经理在辞职加入其最大客户之一后提起诉讼，要求获得该奖金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/morgan-stanley-wins-1-4-million-french-bonus-spat-with-banker-who-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 14:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
